  Link copied!\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 972, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share  Link copied!\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 993, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share  Tom Cruisehas a new face, critics argued on social media following the2024 Paris Olympic Games closing ceremonyon Sunday (August 11).\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1135, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TheMission: Impossiblestardescended from the top of the Stade de France after H.E.R.\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1214, \"end\": 1220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H.E.R.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.045920946101906e-48, \"text\": \"H.E.R.\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H.E.R.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H.E.R.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"sangThe Star-Spangled Banner.\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1250, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His dramatic sky-diving and motorcycle-riding tricks stunned athletes and fans alike.\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1336, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After walking through a sea of competitors, Simone Biles and Los Angeles Mayor Karen Bass handed the 62-year-old, notable for doing his own stunts, the Olympic flag for him to bring back to the US,Fox Newsreported on Sunday.\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1384, \"end\": 1396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}, {\"begin\": 1401, \"end\": 1412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0375088440670565e-22, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 1419, \"end\": 1429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Karen Bass\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\"}, {\"begin\": 1534, \"end\": 1536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997140717649303, \"rank\": 0.00026417913464063254, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1537, \"end\": 1540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"score\": 0.952799737938772, \"rank\": 0.049538367354189455, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The next Summer Olympics will take place in Los Angeles,USA, from Friday, July 14, 2028, to Sunday, July 30, 2028.\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1680, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1610, \"end\": 1621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0375088440670565e-22, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 1622, \"end\": 1625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9845904438158658, \"rank\": 0.015650726940505944, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a pre-recorded clip, Tom rode through the French capital city and onto a plane before he made his way to the top of the Hollywood sign in the City of Angels, which was configured to show theOlympicrings, as perFox News.\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1904, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1727, \"end\": 1746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French capital city\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1805, \"end\": 1819, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Image credits:Fabrizio Bensch- Pool/Getty Images  And despite astonishing viewers with his performance, a handful of people also noticed that the actor's face was visibly different, as an X user (formerly known as Twitter) commented: \\\"DidTom Cruisehave work done on his face?\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 2183, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1944, \"end\": 1949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.999999999397005, \"rank\": 6.030960186665566e-10, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}, {\"begin\": 2122, \"end\": 2129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2344732062483225e-39, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At 1st glance, he resembled Don Johnson.\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2226, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2214, \"end\": 2217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Don_Draper\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.942809629544834e-17, \"text\": \"Don\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Don_Draper\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Don_Draper\"}, {\"begin\": 2218, \"end\": 2225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"score\": 0.9999999999818101, \"rank\": 1.8039092151222028e-11, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asking for a friend.\\\"\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2248, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A person wrote: \\\"What in the narcissism isTom Cruiseand his bloated face doing up there?\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2338, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sir get down before you break a hip.\\\"\", \"from\": 2339, \"to\": 2376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Image credits:Jamie Squire/Getty Images  \\\"Tom Cruiseappears to have overdone the fillers a bit,\\\" a netizen noted.\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2493, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2407, \"end\": 2412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.999999999397005, \"rank\": 6.030960186665566e-10, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dermal fillers are gel-like substances that are injected beneath the skin to restore lost volume, smooth lines and soften creases, or enhance facial contours,the American Board of Cosmetic Surgery states.\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2699, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"According to the board, more than 1 million men and women choose this popular facial rejuvenation treatment annually.\", \"from\": 2701, \"to\": 2818, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Image credits:Fabrizio Bensch- Pool/Getty Images  A separate individual chimed in: \\\"Tom Cruise has WAY too much Botox.\\\"\", \"from\": 2822, \"to\": 2941, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2858, \"end\": 2863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.999999999397005, \"rank\": 6.030960186665566e-10, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}, {\"begin\": 2906, \"end\": 2916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}, {\"begin\": 2934, \"end\": 2939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botulinum_toxin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Botox\", \"types\": [\"Q8386\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botulinum_toxin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botulinum_toxin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The most popular type of injectable fillers are made of hyaluronic acid and tend to be the most temporary option.\", \"from\": 2943, \"to\": 3056, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hyaluronic acid fillers typically last from 6 to 18 months.\", \"from\": 3057, \"to\": 3116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Botulinum toxin injections, such as Botox, relax the muscles in your face to smooth out lines and wrinkles, such as crow's feet and frown lines,the NHS explains.\", \"from\": 3118, \"to\": 3279, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3154, \"end\": 3159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botulinum_toxin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Botox\", \"types\": [\"Q8386\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botulinum_toxin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botulinum_toxin\"}, {\"begin\": 3266, \"end\": 3269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Health_Service\", \"score\": 0.9999999998653948, \"rank\": 1.342643023883268e-10, \"text\": \"NHS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Health_Service\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Health_Service\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Image credits:tomcruise  Overuse of both Botox and fillers can lead to negative effects.\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3371, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3324, \"end\": 3329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botulinum_toxin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Botox\", \"types\": [\"Q8386\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botulinum_toxin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botulinum_toxin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to Nurse Gemavie, overdosing on Botox can lead to excessive muscle weakness, which can cause problems with facial expression and lead to an unnatural appearance.\", \"from\": 3372, \"to\": 3543, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3414, \"end\": 3419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botulinum_toxin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Botox\", \"types\": [\"Q8386\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botulinum_toxin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botulinum_toxin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom has likely undergone a face-lift at some point in his life, combined with fat grafting, according to a consultant plastic surgeon, Kshem Yapa.\", \"from\": 3545, \"to\": 3691, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kshem toldThe Daily Mailon Monday (August 12): \\\"It can be an effective combination, and it's an operation I frequently do myself, but you have to take care with the amount of fat you put into the face.\", \"from\": 3693, \"to\": 3894, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The only thing more stretched out than this closing ceremony is Tom Cruise's new facepic.twitter.com/eriVaDb3dd  - Glenn Scott (@glenrules)August 11, 2024    Wait.\", \"from\": 3896, \"to\": 4059, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3960, \"end\": 3970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}, {\"begin\": 4011, \"end\": 4022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenn_Scott\", \"score\": 0.9999898843727848, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Glenn Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenn_Scott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenn_Scott\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom Cruise has a new face.\", \"from\": 4060, \"to\": 4086, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4060, \"end\": 4070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"- stargirl.\", \"from\": 4088, \"to\": 4099, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(@thetoidoll)August 11, 2024    \\\"As we age, two things happen - we develop skin laxity, so the face droops and you see deeper nose-to-mouth lines, jowls, and a loose neck.\", \"from\": 4100, \"to\": 4271, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We also lose volume, from around the temples and mid-face, which can lead to a more gaunt appearance.\", \"from\": 4273, \"to\": 4375, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, we are NOT going to discuss Tom Cruise's face last night at the Olympics closing ceremony?\", \"from\": 4377, \"to\": 4471, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4409, \"end\": 4419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was just me?\", \"from\": 4472, \"to\": 4487, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Oookay then.#tomcruiseolympics  - ThatGuy (@The_Habe)August 13, 2024    \\\"Afaceliftmoves the facial tissue back into their more youthful position, while fat - taken from elsewhere in the body, usually the stomach or flanks, and placed into the face using tiny injections - supplements lost volume.\", \"from\": 4488, \"to\": 4784, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But those fat grafts will still behave like stomach fat, even in the face.\", \"from\": 4786, \"to\": 4861, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So we warn patients if they put on weight, they will put it on in their face quite visibly.\", \"from\": 4862, \"to\": 4953, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You also have to be judicious in how much you graft into the face, for this reason.\\\"\", \"from\": 4955, \"to\": 5040, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Was that Tom Cruise or Sandi Toksvig?#ClosingCeremony#Olympics#Olympics2024Parispic.twitter.com/DegGHDLq5j  - Wokey McWokeface \\ud83c\\udf39\\ud83d\\udc99 (@WokeyMcWokefac3)August 12, 2024    The expert in facelift surgery agreed there was a \\\"characteristic look\\\" to over-done fat transfer to the face, as he explained: \\\"It's a puffy, mask-like appearance where the mid-face does not move.\\\"\", \"from\": 5042, \"to\": 5407, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5051, \"end\": 5061, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Othercosmetic surgeonshave dubbed the effect a \\\"Howdy Doody face\\\" - referring to an American wooden puppet show character that was the star of a 1960s television show,The Daily Mailreported.\", \"from\": 5409, \"to\": 5599, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5495, \"end\": 5503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9995591720417574, \"rank\": 0.00041887720044030585, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The puppet had exaggerated facial features, and it was once described as the \\\"ugliest puppet imaginable.\\\"\", \"from\": 5601, \"to\": 5706, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How'd that lady almost make out with Tom Cruise on international TV \\ud83d\\ude02#ClosingCeremonypic.twitter.com/IxtmIUPdcA  - Georgia Rose \\ud83c\\uddff\\ud83c\\udde6 \\ud83c\\udf49 (@Rasheeda_S)August 11, 2024    With his boyish good looks and absence of frown lines, plastic surgery rumors have dogged the actor for years,The Sunreported in 2022.\", \"from\": 5708, \"to\": 6007, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5747, \"end\": 5757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although he has reportedly consistently deniedgoing under the knife, fans have speculated the ever-youthful star has had a nose job, hair transplant, and Botox, as well as veneers on his teeth.\", \"from\": 6009, \"to\": 6202, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When Tom starred inThe Outsidersin 1982, his teeth were visibly yellowed and misaligned, with a pronounced overbite, as perThe Sun.\", \"from\": 6204, \"to\": 6335, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Image credits:Nancy Moran/Sygma/Getty Images  Upon booking leading roles, such as Maverick inTop Gun, Tom reportedly had his teeth whitened to improve the look.\", \"from\": 6339, \"to\": 6499, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6359, \"end\": 6370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nancy_Moran\", \"score\": 0.9999976591916605, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nancy Moran\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nancy_Moran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nancy_Moran\"}, {\"begin\": 6371, \"end\": 6376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sygma_(agency)\", \"score\": 0.9634108711081808, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sygma\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sygma_(agency)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sygma_(agency)\"}, {\"begin\": 6377, \"end\": 6382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.999999999397005, \"rank\": 6.030960186665566e-10, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It wasn't until 2001, after splitting from Nicole Kidman, that Tom got braces to rectify his overbite, proudly showing them off at the premiere ofMinority Report, as per the British tabloid.\", \"from\": 6501, \"to\": 6691, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6550, \"end\": 6563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicole_Kidman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.315805564906978e-69, \"text\": \"Nicole Kidman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicole_Kidman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicole_Kidman\"}, {\"begin\": 6681, \"end\": 6688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9981736098805932, \"rank\": 0.0018297319202710577, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By 2010, Tom's face was reportedly beginning to change, occasionally looking chubbier, possibly due to weight fluctuation.\", \"from\": 6693, \"to\": 6815, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Image credits:Alain BENAINOUS/Gamma-Rapho/Getty Images  Rumors that theGolden Globe awardswinner had undergone a nose job began back in 2012, but when asked byPlayboymagazine if he had ever had surgery, he replied: \\\"I have not and never would.\\\"\", \"from\": 6819, \"to\": 7063, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom's appearance at the 2016 BAFTAs had fans commenting on how he looked \\\"inflated\\\" and \\\"puffy,\\\"The Sunreported.\", \"from\": 7065, \"to\": 7177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At theMission Impossible: Falloutpremiere in 2018, Tom reportedly looked leaner, with more lines showing on his forehead.\", \"from\": 7179, \"to\": 7300, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Image credits:Bill Davila/Getty Images  Such \\\"dramatic\\\" fluctuation may have been because \\\"Cruise had a bit too much fat put in,\\\" Kshem toldThe Daily Mail.\", \"from\": 7304, \"to\": 7459, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7336, \"end\": 7341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.999999999397005, \"rank\": 6.030960186665566e-10, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He explained: \\\"We do not recommend fat grafting is used alone as a filler, without a facelift as you'd have to add so much to achieve an effect there would be a danger patients would be left looking worse.\", \"from\": 7461, \"to\": 7666, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The other thing it's important patients realize is that fat grafts are relatively difficult to undo - other kinds of filler naturally dissolve to some extent over time, but fat is permanent.\", \"from\": 7668, \"to\": 7859, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Image credits:Ken Ishii/Getty Images  \\\"You'd need another operation to remove it.\\\"\", \"from\": 7863, \"to\": 7945, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7883, \"end\": 7892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ken_Ishii\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ken Ishii\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ken_Ishii\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ken_Ishii\"}, {\"begin\": 7893, \"end\": 7898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.999999999397005, \"rank\": 6.030960186665566e-10, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Plastic SurgeonDr.\", \"from\": 7947, \"to\": 7965, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fadi Hamadani toldThe Daily Mail:\\\"Tom Cruise has managed to maintain a remarkably youthful appearance, which many credit to his active lifestyle and commitment to fitness.\", \"from\": 7966, \"to\": 8137, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"While we can not say for certain if he's undergone any cosmetic procedures, it's possible he's chosen non-invasive treatments to keep his refreshed look.\", \"from\": 8139, \"to\": 8293, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Celebritiesoften turn to options like fillers or Botox to reduce wrinkles and restore facial volume.\", \"from\": 8297, \"to\": 8398, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Additionally, advanced procedures like Morpheus8, which blends micro-needling with radiofrequency energy, and FaceTite, a minimally invasive contouring treatment, can also help achieve a more youthful, tightened appearance.\", \"from\": 8400, \"to\": 8624, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These treatments are popular for those aiming to subtly enhance their features while maintaining a natural look.\\\"\", \"from\": 8626, \"to\": 8740, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By entering your email and clicking Subscribe, you are agreeing to let us send you customized marketing messages about us and our advertising partners.\", \"from\": 8766, \"to\": 8917, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are also agreeing to ourPrivacy Policy.\", \"from\": 8918, \"to\": 8961, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you!\", \"from\": 8963, \"to\": 8973, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You have successfully subscribed to newsletters!\", \"from\": 8974, \"to\": 9022, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Anyone can write on Bored Panda.Start writing!\", \"from\": 9024, \"to\": 9070, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Bored Panda onGoogle News!\", \"from\": 9072, \"to\": 9105, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9085, \"end\": 9096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bored_Panda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bored Panda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bored_Panda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bored_Panda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow us onFlipboard.com/@boredpanda!\", \"from\": 9107, \"to\": 9145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"91Kviews  -9  16  -9  16  Link copied!\", \"from\": 9149, \"to\": 9187, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share  Link copied!\", \"from\": 9189, \"to\": 9208, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share  Author,BoredPanda staff  I am a journalist who works as Bored Panda's News Team's Senior Writer.\", \"from\": 9210, \"to\": 9313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9279, \"end\": 9290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bored_Panda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bored Panda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bored_Panda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bored_Panda\"}, {\"begin\": 9279, \"end\": 9290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bored_Panda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bored Panda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bored_Panda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bored_Panda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The news team produces stories focused on pop culture.\", \"from\": 9314, \"to\": 9368, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Whenever I get the opportunity and the time, I investigate and produce my own exclusive stories, where I get to explore a wider range of topics.\", \"from\": 9369, \"to\": 9513, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some examples include: \\\"Doberman Tobias the viral medical service dog\\\" and \\\"The lawyer who brought rare uterine cancer that affects 9/11 victims to light\\\".\", \"from\": 9514, \"to\": 9669, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You have got a tip?\", \"from\": 9670, \"to\": 9689, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"email me: andrea.o@boredpanda.com  Author,BoredPanda staff  I am a journalist who works as Bored Panda's News Team's Senior Writer.\", \"from\": 9690, \"to\": 9821, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9787, \"end\": 9798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bored_Panda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bored Panda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bored_Panda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bored_Panda\"}, {\"begin\": 9787, \"end\": 9798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bored_Panda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bored Panda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bored_Panda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bored_Panda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The news team produces stories focused on pop culture.\", \"from\": 9822, \"to\": 9876, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Whenever I get the opportunity and the time, I investigate and produce my own exclusive stories, where I get to explore a wider range of topics.\", \"from\": 9877, \"to\": 10021, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some examples include: \\\"Doberman Tobias the viral medical service dog\\\" and \\\"The lawyer who brought rare uterine cancer that affects 9/11 victims to light\\\".\", \"from\": 10022, \"to\": 10177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You have got a tip?\", \"from\": 10178, \"to\": 10197, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"email me: andrea.o@boredpanda.com  Author,Community member  Hey there!\", \"from\": 10198, \"to\": 10268, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a Visual Editor in News team.\", \"from\": 10269, \"to\": 10303, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My responsibility is to ensure that you can read the story not just through text, but also through photos.\", \"from\": 10304, \"to\": 10410, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I get to work with a variety of topics ranging from celebrity drama to mind-blowing Nasa cosmic news.\", \"from\": 10411, \"to\": 10512, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And let me tell you, that's what makes this job an absolute blast!\", \"from\": 10513, \"to\": 10579, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Outside of work, you can find me sweating it out in dance classes or unleashing my creativity by drawing and creating digital paintings of different characters that lives in my head.\", \"from\": 10580, \"to\": 10762, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I also love spending time outdoors and play board games with my friends.\", \"from\": 10763, \"to\": 10835, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Author,Community member  Hey there!\", \"from\": 10837, \"to\": 10872, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a Visual Editor in News team.\", \"from\": 10873, \"to\": 10907, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My responsibility is to ensure that you can read the story not just through text, but also through photos.\", \"from\": 10908, \"to\": 11014, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I get to work with a variety of topics ranging from celebrity drama to mind-blowing Nasa cosmic news.\", \"from\": 11015, \"to\": 11116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And let me tell you, that's what makes this job an absolute blast!\", \"from\": 11117, \"to\": 11183, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Outside of work, you can find me sweating it out in dance classes or unleashing my creativity by drawing and creating digital paintings of different characters that lives in my head.\", \"from\": 11184, \"to\": 11366, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I also love spending time outdoors and play board games with my friends.\", \"from\": 11367, \"to\": 11439, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Why they are showboating this controlling, Scientology worshipping freak eludes me.\", \"from\": 11441, \"to\": 11524, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I recently watched the Top Gun sequel (I am not a Cruise fan, I am a fighter jet fan, lol) and I also watched the closing ceremony.\", \"from\": 11526, \"to\": 11657, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He DID look different than he did in TG:M. I know TG:M was filmed in 2018-2019 (so, 6 years ago) but I have also watched my mother age and she's also had a number of plastic surgery procedures done, including fillers and Botox.\", \"from\": 11658, \"to\": 11885, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even though Cruise was \\\"only\\\" 56 when TG:M was filmed (and of course he had the benefits of makeup and all the Hollywood magic in the universe) I can say with some conviction that a person's face does not usually change THAT drastically between age 56 and age 62.\", \"from\": 11886, \"to\": 12149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12003, \"end\": 12012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.122065040881744e-20, \"text\": \"Hollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Again, my mother's had a ton of stuff done to her face over the decades (she can not handle the fact that aging is real and it's happening to her) and I am just sayin', Cruise looked similar to my mother after some of her procedures.\", \"from\": 12150, \"to\": 12383, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes there is edema and inflammation after a procedure, as well, besides the fillers that get injected, causing a very bloated appearance.\", \"from\": 12384, \"to\": 12527, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's exactly what it is.\", \"from\": 12529, \"to\": 12555, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Like it looks swollen, not like he's gained weight but his skin/face are poofy.\", \"from\": 12556, \"to\": 12635, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The man is 62.\", \"from\": 12637, \"to\": 12651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Older than Tom Walz.\", \"from\": 12652, \"to\": 12672, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"About time he started looking it.\", \"from\": 12673, \"to\": 12706, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This comment is hidden.Click here to view.\", \"from\": 12708, \"to\": 12750, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Are you seriously comparing Tom Cruise to A-Walz ( a politician you'd probably never heard of before a week ago, but now likely worship as the greatest VP candidate ever)  Why they are showboating this controlling, Scientology worshipping freak eludes me.\", \"from\": 12752, \"to\": 13007, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12786, \"end\": 12796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}, {\"begin\": 12786, \"end\": 12796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I recently watched the Top Gun sequel (I am not a Cruise fan, I am a fighter jet fan, lol) and I also watched the closing ceremony.\", \"from\": 13009, \"to\": 13140, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He DID look different than he did in TG:M. I know TG:M was filmed in 2018-2019 (so, 6 years ago) but I have also watched my mother age and she's also had a number of plastic surgery procedures done, including fillers and Botox.\", \"from\": 13141, \"to\": 13368, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even though Cruise was \\\"only\\\" 56 when TG:M was filmed (and of course he had the benefits of makeup and all the Hollywood magic in the universe) I can say with some conviction that a person's face does not usually change THAT drastically between age 56 and age 62.\", \"from\": 13369, \"to\": 13632, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13486, \"end\": 13495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.122065040881744e-20, \"text\": \"Hollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Again, my mother's had a ton of stuff done to her face over the decades (she can not handle the fact that aging is real and it's happening to her) and I am just sayin', Cruise looked similar to my mother after some of her procedures.\", \"from\": 13633, \"to\": 13866, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes there is edema and inflammation after a procedure, as well, besides the fillers that get injected, causing a very bloated appearance.\", \"from\": 13867, \"to\": 14010, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's exactly what it is.\", \"from\": 14012, \"to\": 14038, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Like it looks swollen, not like he's gained weight but his skin/face are poofy.\", \"from\": 14039, \"to\": 14118, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The man is 62.\", \"from\": 14120, \"to\": 14134, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Older than Tom Walz.\", \"from\": 14135, \"to\": 14155, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"About time he started looking it.\", \"from\": 14156, \"to\": 14189, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This comment is hidden.Click here to view.\", \"from\": 14191, \"to\": 14233, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Are you seriously comparing Tom Cruise to A-Walz ( a politician you'd probably never heard of before a week ago, but now likely worship as the greatest VP candidate ever)\", \"from\": 14235, \"to\": 14405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14269, \"end\": 14279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}, {\"begin\": 14269, \"end\": 14279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}]}]}"